Main Event Loop:
On VS Code Activation:
  Load user data from storage.
  Initialize side panel with tabs (XP, Badges, Eco Tips, Leaderboard).
  Start Eco Tips Engine (language-specific scanners).

On Debugger Session:
  Listen for debugger events (breakpoints, errors).
  If bug is fixed (test passes):
    AddXP(10, "bug_fixed")
    CheckAchievements()

On File Save:
  If eco-tips enabled:
    Scan code for language-specific inefficiencies.
    For each detected issue:
      Show eco tip in "Problems" pane.
    If user applies tip (via Quick Fix):
      AddXP(5, "eco_tip_applied")
      CheckAchievements()

On Manual Scan (Command Palette):
  Trigger full codebase eco-tip scan.
